<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,1664,1977]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,270,1880,1905]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Head.</emphasis>
Face occupying about 
<number box="[530,541,1880,1904]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" value="1.0">1</number>
/ 
<number box="[551,565,1880,1904]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" value="3.0">3</number>
of head width in frontal view; yellow; yellow pilose. Gena yellow. Frons and vertex brown; yellow pilose. Occiput brown; yellow pilose dorsally, white pilose ventrally. Eye bare. Antennal fossa about as high as wide. Antenna black; antennal ratio approximately as 
<number box="[1007,1026,1952,1976]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" value="2.0">2</number>
: 
<number box="[1030,1042,1952,1976]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" value="1.0">1</number>
: 
<number box="[1047,1067,1952,1976]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41" value="4.0">4</number>
.
</paragraph>
